or: #ffffff;\">花下一禾生</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; background-color: #ffffff;\">去之為惡草</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"d-flex align-items-end\"><cite title=\"неизвестен\"><a id=\"biblio_poems\" href=\"http://chinavsem.ucoz.ru/forum/16-112-6\">Источник: сайт http://chinavsem.ucoz.ru/forum/16-112-6</a></cite></div>',NULL,NULL),(88,113,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'小阁藏春','\"В маленький терем проникла и притаилась Весна …\"','ЛЦЧ-4',248,'\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">小阁藏春，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">闲窗锁昼，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">画堂无限深幽。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">篆香烧尽，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">日影下帘钩。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">手种江梅更好</span>,</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">又何必、</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">临水登楼。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">无人到，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">寂寥浑似，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">何逊在扬州。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">从来，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">知韵胜，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">难堪雨藉，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">不耐风柔。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">更谁家横笛，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">吹动浓愁。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">莫恨香消雪减，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">须信道、</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">扫迹情留。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">难言处，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">良宵淡月，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">疏影尚风流。</span></p>\n',NULL,NULL),(89,113,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'风定落花深','\"С веток осыпав цветы, ветер проносся и стих…\"','ЛЦЧ-5',248,'\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">风定落花深，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">帘外拥红堆雪。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">长记海棠开後，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">正是伤春时节。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">酒阑歌罢玉尊空，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">青缸暗明灭。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">魂梦不堪幽怨，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">更一声啼鴂。</span></p>\n',NULL,NULL),(90,113,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'草际鸣蛩','\"Где-то в траве, на меже громко сверчки залились …\"','ЛЦЧ-6',248,'<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">草际鸣蛩。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">惊落梧桐。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">正人间、</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">天上愁浓。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">云阶月地，</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">关锁千重。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">纵浮槎来，</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">浮槎去，</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">不相逢。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">星桥鹊驾，</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">经年才见，</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">想离情、</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">别恨难穷。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">牵牛织女，</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">莫是离中。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">甚霎儿晴，</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">霎儿风</span>.</p>',NULL,NULL),(91,113,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'落日熔金','\"Расплавленное золото заката…\"','ЛЦЧ-7',233,'\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">落日熔金，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">暮云合璧，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">人在何处。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">染柳烟浓，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">吹梅笛怨，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">春意知几许。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">元宵佳节，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">融和天气，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">次第岂无风雨。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">来相召、</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">香车宝马，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">谢他酒朋诗侣。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">中州盛日，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">闺门多暇，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">记得偏重三五。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">铺翠冠儿，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">捻金雪柳，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">逢带争济楚。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">如今憔悴，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">风鬟霜鬓，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">怕见夜间出去。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">不如向、</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">帘儿底下，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">听人笑语。</span></p>\n',NULL,NULL),(92,113,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'常记溪亭日暮','\"Вижу снова простор голубой…\"','ЛЦЧ-1',248,'\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">常记溪亭日暮，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">沉醉不知归路，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">兴尽晚回</span><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">舟</span><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">误入藕花深处。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">争渡，争渡，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">惊起一滩鸥鹭</span></p>',NULL,NULL),(93,199,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'月夜行黄沙道中','Ночью на пути в Хуанша','СЦЦ-3',248,'\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">明月别枝惊鹊，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">清风半夜鸣蝉。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">稻花香里说丰年，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">听取蛙声一片。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">七八个星天外，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">两三点雨山前。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">旧时茅店社林边，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">路转溪桥忽见。</span></p>\n',NULL,NULL),(94,199,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'山寺夜半闻钟','В храме в полночь раздается звон колокола','СЦЦ-2',248,'\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">身世酒杯中。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">万事皆空。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">古来三五个英雄。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">雨打风吹何处是</span>,</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">汉殿秦宫。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">梦入少年丛。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">歌舞匆匆。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">老僧夜半误鸣钟。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">惊志西窗眠不得，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">卷地西风。</span></p>\n',NULL,NULL),(95,199,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'六十三年无限事','Эти стихи написал в год жэньсюй, в день моего рождения, и выразил в них свои чувства (\"Я шестьдесят три долгих года прожил…\")','СЦЦ-7',248,'<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">六十三年无限事，</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">从头悔恨难追。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">已知六十二年非。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">只应今日是，</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">后日又寻思。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">少是多非惟有酒，</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">何须过后方知。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">从今休似去年时。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">病中留客饮，</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">醉里和人诗。</span></p>',NULL,NULL),(96,199,'书博山道中壁','\"Пишу на стене по дороге в Бошань\"',NULL,NULL,'1. 少年不识愁滋味','\"В годы юные, помнится, было мне жаль…\"','СЦЦ-1',248,'\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">少年不识愁滋味，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">爱上层楼；</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">爱上层楼，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">为</span><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">赋</span><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">下</span><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">来</span><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">强</span><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">说</span><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">愁</span><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">而今识得愁滋味，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">欲说还休；</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">欲说还休，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">却道天凉好个秋。</span></p>\n',NULL,NULL),(97,199,'书博山道中壁','\"Пишу на стене по дороге в Бошань\"',NULL,NULL,'2. 烟迷露麦荒池柳','\"Вот растаял туман. На пшенице роса …\"','СЦЦ-6',248,'\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">烟迷露麦荒池柳，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">洗雨烘晴。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">洗雨烘晴。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">一样春风几样青。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">提壶脱袴催归去，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">万恨千情。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">万恨千情。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">各自无聊各自鸣</span></p>',NULL,NULL),(98,48,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'忆菊','Думы о хризантеме','ВИ-1',248,'\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">插在长颈的虾青瓷的瓶里，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">六方的水晶瓶里的菊花，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">攒在紫藤仙姑篮里的菊花；</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">守着酒壶的菊花，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">陪着螯盏的菊花；</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">未放，将放，半放，盛放的菊花。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">镶着金边的绛色的鸡爪菊；</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">粉红色的碎瓣的绣球菊！</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">懒慵慵的江西腊哟；</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">倒挂着一饼蜂窠似的黄心，</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">仿佛是朵紫的向日葵呢。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">长瓣抱心，密瓣平顶的菊花；</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">…</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">啊！东方底花，骚人逸士底花呀</span>!</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:SimSun\">那东方底诗魂陶元亮</span></p>\n<p><span style=\